  "summary": "SOAPpy vulnerable to XXE attacks",
  "details": "SOAPpy 0.12.5 does not properly detect recursion during entity expansion, which allows remote attackers to cause a denial of service (memory and CPU consumption) via a crafted SOAP request containing a large number of nested entity references.",
